name: MSStickerBrowserViewDataSource
desc: The protocol for dynamically providing stickers to a browser view.

items.name: func numberOfStickers(in: MSStickerBrowserView) -> Int
items.desc: Asks the data source for the number of stickers that the browser will display.

items.name: func stickerBrowserView(MSStickerBrowserView, stickerAt: Int) -> MSSticker
items.desc: Asks the data source for the sticker object that the browser will display at the provided index.
